    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted F80-generation M3 powered by the S55 3.0L twin-mono-scroll turbocharged inline-six. This powerplant delivers a broad torque plateau and immediate throttle response, coupled with a 7-speed M-DCT that provides crisp, rev-matched downshifts. The vehicle features the Active M Differential and a CFRP drive shaft, ensuring optimal power delivery and reduced rotational mass. The suspension geometry remains true, providing excellent kinematic feedback through the steering rack. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and light patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the internal components\u2014including the cooling system and high-pressure fuel pumps\u2014are in excellent working order. This is a high-performance specimen optimized for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain health and chassis dynamics.",
