      "description": "This 2019 BMW 530i is the perfect blend of performance and executive comfort. Finished in a sophisticated Alpine White, the exterior maintains a brilliant shine, showing only the minor stone chips expected from light highway use. Inside, the Canberra Beige Dakota leather remains supple and free of tears or heavy creasing, preserved in a strictly smoke-free environment. Every feature, from the high-resolution navigation system to the multi-zone climate control, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this vehicle has been meticulously cared for, with a complete service history from authorized centers. We recently performed a comprehensive inspection and oil service, and the Continental tires still offer plenty of life for the road ahead. This car delivers a smooth, quiet, and powerful driving experience, making it an excellent choice for someone seeking luxury without the new-car depreciation. Ready for its next owner with two sets of keys and all original manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
